<h2>How to Choose the Right Extension</h2>
<p><strong>Ask yourself:</strong></p>
<ol>
<li>What is my primary use case? (writing, research, email, coding)</li>
<li>How much do I use ChatGPT daily? (light use = free tier, heavy use = premium)</li>
<li>Do I need current web data, or is the base model enough?</li>
<li>Do I work primarily in specific apps (Gmail, Google Docs) or across the web?</li>
</ol>
